author: Stephanie Ebbs, Cheyenne Haslett
title: Indian Country faces higher risks, lack of resources in COVID-19 fight
description: As the number of COVID19 cases in the Navajo Nation climbs, experts say they're concerned about the high risk of transmission in Indian Country,
content:
As the death toll from coronavirus rises in Navajo nation, experts closest to the crisis are tragically finding themselves the least surprised.
